16
00:02:02,330 --> 00:02:03,370
I'm sorry.

17
00:02:03,370 --> 00:02:06,210
I didn't know you'd have a guest.

18
00:02:06,210 --> 00:02:07,800
Hello.

19
00:02:08,340 --> 00:02:09,930
I'm...

20
00:02:09,930 --> 00:02:13,490
He's the person I'm seeing.

21
00:02:14,430 --> 00:02:15,680
Oh...

22
00:02:18,210 --> 00:02:20,660
I'm Na Aejoon.

23
00:02:20,660 --> 00:02:22,880
I'm Yeon Jooha.

24
00:02:24,280 --> 00:02:27,760
I used to live here.

25
00:02:27,760 --> 00:02:28,730
Sorry?

26
00:02:28,730 --> 00:02:30,740
The place was put up for rent,

27
00:02:30,740 --> 00:02:34,079
but he moved in
and didn't change the password.

28
00:02:34,079 --> 00:02:36,900
He said it's too troublesome.

29
00:02:36,900 --> 00:02:38,770
Oh, I see.

30
00:02:38,770 --> 00:02:41,600
He'll be a guest on my radio show
in a few days,

31
00:02:41,600 --> 00:02:44,490
but he isn't even aware
of the script changes.

32
00:02:44,490 --> 00:02:47,620
That's why I came to give this to him
on behalf of the manager.

33
00:02:47,620 --> 00:02:50,230
Please forgive this intrusion.
It won't happen again.

34
00:02:50,230 --> 00:02:52,700
Oh, no, it's okay.

35
00:02:52,700 --> 00:02:56,370
