36
00:02:57,770 --> 00:03:02,160
Well, being close and being in love
are different.

37
00:03:05,170 --> 00:03:08,090
Alright, enjoy your time together.

38
00:03:08,090 --> 00:03:10,340
See you again sometime.

39
00:03:10,340 --> 00:03:13,680
And I'll see you at the radio studio,
Mr. Choi Siyeol!

40
00:03:21,630 --> 00:03:23,500
Wow.

41
00:03:23,500 --> 00:03:26,040
I actually saw Yeon Jooha up close.

42
00:03:26,040 --> 00:03:28,000
Sit down.

43
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:35,460
Let's talk about us again.

44
00:03:35,460 --> 00:03:37,190
It's quite late already.

45
00:03:37,190 --> 00:03:39,190
