55
00:04:22,810 --> 00:04:25,890
Oh... It's okay. I'm used to it.

56
00:04:25,890 --> 00:04:29,140
But I think it's really impressive.

57
00:04:29,140 --> 00:04:32,270
They say celebrities
all watch what they eat,

58
00:04:32,270 --> 00:04:35,540
