72
00:05:20,470 --> 00:05:21,650
Please.

73
00:05:21,650 --> 00:05:24,580
Just stay one more night, okay?

74
00:05:25,490 --> 00:05:30,340
I'll make you delicious salad
tomorrow morning then.

75
00:06:18,500 --> 00:06:20,460
What are you doing?

76
00:06:43,460 --> 00:06:45,840
This is so embarrassing.

77
00:06:46,470 --> 00:06:48,300
Just kill me now.

78
00:06:53,050 --> 00:06:58,800
Wait. So you were eating it secretly
because of what I said?

79
00:07:00,210 --> 00:07:01,840
Stop laughing at me.

80
00:07:01,840 --> 00:07:03,230
The thought of you

81
00:07:03,230 --> 00:07:06,030
sneaking out to buy instant noodles
and eating it secretly

82
00:07:06,030 --> 00:07:07,770
is just too funny.

83
00:07:17,530 --> 00:07:20,640
You could've just said
you were craving instant noodles.

84
00:07:20,640 --> 00:07:23,100
Eat up.

85
00:07:36,390 --> 00:07:37,970
Are you okay?

86
00:07:37,970 --> 00:07:39,480
Water.

87
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:48,490
So cute.

88
00:07:52,670 --> 00:07:54,740
