90
00:08:02,190 --> 00:08:03,810
Are you okay?

91
00:08:04,310 --> 00:08:05,670
Want more water?

92
00:08:05,670 --> 00:08:06,410
Are you okay?

93
00:08:06,410 --> 00:08:08,830
Sometimes,

94
00:08:08,830 --> 00:08:12,380
