99
00:08:36,549 --> 00:08:39,860
Welcome to "Afternoon Melody."
I'm your host, Yeon Jooha.

100
00:08:50,700 --> 00:08:53,130
Let's welcome our guest today,

101
00:08:53,130 --> 00:08:55,200
