102
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:56,820
Hello, everyone.

103
00:08:58,090 --> 00:09:01,410
Hello, I'm Choi Siyeol of A-One.

104
00:09:01,410 --> 00:09:04,810
Hello, I'm JJ,
the all-round leader of A-One.

105
00:09:04,810 --> 00:09:08,310
Hello, I'm Kyutae, the rapper of A-One.

106
00:09:08,270 --> 00:09:11,360
[Ji Kyusung, are you at
the radio studio now?]

107
00:09:15,270 --> 00:09:18,350
[Yeah, why?
I didn't see you all weekend.]

108
00:09:18,350 --> 00:09:21,430
[I doubt you're asking for autographs.]

109
00:09:21,430 --> 00:09:25,670
[I want to get there
by the end of the broadcast.]

110
00:09:25,670 --> 00:09:28,690
[You were together all day,
but you already miss him?]

111
00:09:28,690 --> 00:09:33,970
