That you were his longtime fanboy?]

113
00:09:38,040 --> 00:09:40,440
[What? I wasn't a fanboy...]

114
00:09:40,440 --> 00:09:42,850
[I was just... a fan.]

115
00:09:42,850 --> 00:09:45,130
[It's stupid that I'm hiding
that we're relatives.]

116
00:09:45,130 --> 00:09:47,110
[It's like I'm always lying to him.]

117
00:09:47,110 --> 00:09:49,010
[It's about time I be honest with him.]

118
00:09:49,010 --> 00:09:52,980
[Dude, it's not a big deal.
Don't get all serious.]

119
00:09:52,980 --> 00:09:55,950
[I'll send you the address.
Call me when you arrive.]

120
00:10:00,950 --> 00:10:03,530
