123
00:10:10,830 --> 00:10:13,020
Kyutae's the top scorer so far.

124
00:10:13,020 --> 00:10:16,190
Last but not least, Siyeol,
want to give it a go?

125
00:10:16,190 --> 00:10:16,900
Of course.

126
00:10:16,900 --> 00:10:19,020
I'm the ace of the group.

127
00:10:19,020 --> 00:10:20,620
Wow, very confident.

128
00:10:20,620 --> 00:10:24,470
Alright. Let's have our next caller.

129
00:10:26,280 --> 00:10:28,400
Hello, this is
Yeon Jooha's "Afternoon Melody."

130
00:10:28,400 --> 00:10:29,280
I'm...

131
00:10:29,280 --> 00:10:30,160
Holy crap!

132
00:10:30,160 --> 00:10:32,730
Aren't you Choi Siyeol?

133
00:10:32,730 --> 00:10:33,990
Yes, I'm Choi Siyeol.

134
00:10:33,990 --> 00:10:34,900
Hello.

135
00:10:34,900 --> 00:10:36,790
It's really Choi Siyeol!

136
00:10:36,790 --> 00:10:38,780
It's really him, you idiot!

137
00:10:38,780 --> 00:10:40,670
Give it to me! Hey!

138
00:10:40,670 --> 00:10:41,900
-Hello?
-Give it to me!

139
00:10:41,900 --> 00:10:43,570
