150
00:11:10,540 --> 00:11:11,900
What the hell?

151
00:11:11,900 --> 00:11:14,460
That's why A-One's debut was postponed

152
00:11:14,460 --> 00:11:18,300
and their image was totally ruined,
all because of him.

153
00:11:18,300 --> 00:11:21,580
Is it even possible to stay friends
with a traitor like that?

154
00:11:21,580 --> 00:11:22,950
-Hey, this is notâ€”
-Hold on.

155
00:11:22,950 --> 00:11:25,870
If you wanted to be an actor,
why join the group in the first place?

156
00:11:25,870 --> 00:11:26,800
That's so selfish.

157
00:11:26,800 --> 00:11:27,900
Please end the call.

158
00:11:27,900 --> 00:11:28,680
Hang on.

159
00:11:28,680 --> 00:11:29,960
Please end the call now!

160
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:31,950
Honestly, I'm more objective

161
00:11:31,910 --> 00:11:34,580
[Say that the time's up and end the call.]

162
00:11:31,950 --> 00:11:34,670
because I'm not a fan.

163
00:11:34,670 --> 00:11:36,070
His ankle injury was also

164
00:11:36,070 --> 00:11:38,060
just a fake excuse to stop the backlash,

165
00:11:38,060 --> 00:11:39,310
wasn't it?

166
00:11:39,310 --> 00:11:42,870
A fake excuse to stop the backlash?

167
00:11:42,870 --> 00:11:43,980
Sorry, due to time constraintsâ€”

168
00:11:43,980 --> 00:11:46,030
So, are you saying

169
00:11:46,030 --> 00:11:50,640
