based on our agency's statement.

184
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:55,250
[9 years ago]

185
00:12:54,060 --> 00:12:56,260
Guys, I'm here.

186
00:12:56,260 --> 00:12:58,630
It was a road we crossed every day.

187
00:12:58,630 --> 00:13:00,350
Hurry up!

188
00:13:00,350 --> 00:13:06,560
I was beside Jooha then,
when we were crossing the road.

189
00:13:19,040 --> 00:13:24,880
If only the drunk driver
didn't speed toward the crosswalk...

190
00:13:26,030 --> 00:13:29,560
If only I shielded Jooha
from the collision...

191
00:13:32,230 --> 00:13:34,540
instead of the other way around...

192
00:13:43,550 --> 00:13:46,180
Then maybe

193
00:13:46,180 --> 00:13:50,840
Yeon Jooha would've debuted with A-One.

194
00:13:52,150 --> 00:13:53,840
What the...

195
00:13:53,840 --> 00:13:57,550
So, please don't ever
make such careless judgements again.

196
00:13:57,550 --> 00:14:00,330
