and abandoned Yeon Jooha.

223
00:16:47,240 --> 00:16:50,410
What, now you regret it?

224
00:16:50,410 --> 00:16:51,370
Hey, Choi Siyeol!

225
00:16:51,370 --> 00:16:54,310
If that's not it,

226
00:16:54,310 --> 00:16:57,240
