238
00:17:42,680 --> 00:17:46,420
you hit on Na Aejoon because you think

239
00:17:46,420 --> 00:17:48,850
he and I are dating?

240
00:17:48,850 --> 00:17:50,850
Yeah.

241
00:17:50,850 --> 00:17:54,400
I hope you'll end up with

242
00:17:54,400 --> 00:17:58,400
